
This perl script sends out POC duty notification.

Dir: /data/mta4/CUS/www/Usint/ 
See also: https://cxc.cfa.harvard.edu/mta_days/mta_script_list/USINT/ti_send_tpoc_duty.html

Script:
-------
send_tpoc_duty.perl

Data:
-----

/data/mta4/CUS/www/Usint/ocat/Info_save/too_contact_info/personal_list
/data/mta4/CUS/www/Usint/ocat/Info_save/too_contact_info/schedule

Output:
-------
email sent out


Cron job:
---------
r2d2-v as cus
0 16 * * * cd /data/mta4/CUS/www/Usint; /usr/local/bin/perl /data/mta4/CUS/www/Usint/send_tpoc_duty.perl >> $HOME/Logs/send_tpoc_duty.cron

